
A clean and interactive weather application

 Features
* Search weather by city
* Get weather using current location
* Interactive map with live weather markers
* Toggle between Celsius & Fahrenheit
* Hourly forecast (next 24 hours)
* 5-day forecast with selectable days
* Recently searched cities (saved in localStorage)
* Dynamic background based on weather
* Extreme heat alert (>40°C)

---

## Tech Stack

* HTML
* Tailwind CSS
* JavaScript (Vanilla)
* OpenWeatherMap API

---

# Setup Instructions

1. Clone the repo:

2. Open `index.html` in your browser

3. Replace API key in JS:

## API Used

* Current Weather:

```
https://api.openweathermap.org/data/2.5/weather
```

* 5 Day / 3 Hour Forecast:

```
https://api.openweathermap.org/data/2.5/forecast
```
